         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">8th March. [187]1. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor by direction of the above Committee to acknowledge your letters of the 19th and 28th of Feby and of the 7th of March ¶  and in reply to inform you that t...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">71.03.08</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Marcus Clarke</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Letter no. 52/I.T.M.71, Outward letterbook 1870-9 pp. 157, Industrial and Technological Museum and Public Library, Museum Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">8th March. [187]1.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor by direction of the above Committee to acknowledge your letters of the 19th and 28th of Feby and of the 7th of March<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to S. Bindon, 19 February 1871; M to M. Clarke, 28 February 1871 (in this edition as 71-02-28a); and M to M. Clarke, 7 March 1871 (in this edition as 71-03-07a).</p>
               </note> and in reply to inform you that the Committee approve of the form of label enclosed for their inspection but think that one dozen for each kind would be sufficient for the present requirements of the Museum. Messrs Clarson &amp; Massina's being the cheaper tender, the Committee would wish for to obtain the dozen sets of each label from that firm<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In fact, for the dozen labels the committee had decided was enough, Clarson &amp; Massina's tender price was the same as Mason Firth &amp; McCuthcheon's, but for larger numbers it was more expensive than theirs! See </seg>M to M. Clarke, 7 March 1871 (in this edition as 71-03-07a).</p>
                  <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient Servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Marcus Clarke</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Secretary</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">The Director</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanic Gardens</p>
